imageDescriptions.description: WIDE SHOT of a regal throne room. LIGHTING: warm candlelight mixed with dramatic shadows. FOREGROUND: Alexander (medium brown wavy hair, green eyes, casual hoodie) and Adrian (short curly ginger hair, bright sky-blue eyes, casual jacket) stand nervously near a boastful miller. MIDGROUND: the king sits high on a carved throne, eager and threatening, golden decorations glinting. BACKGROUND: courtiers in muted colors whisper, tall banners, stone pillars. MOOD: tense, ominous, slightly whimsical. STYLE: Watercolor illustration style, Axel Scheffler inspired. Include subtle magical glow near the children's hands.

CLOSE-UP of a dim chamber full of straw and an old spinning wheel. LIGHTING: candlelit, warm highlights with deep shadows. FOREGROUND: Alexander (tousled medium brown hair, green eyes) hands trembling over a thin necklace and a ring; Adrian (short curly ginger hair, sky-blue eyes) crouched nearby, worried. MIDGROUND: Brumm the Stoneguard, large stone form with glowing red eyes, watches solemnly. BACKGROUND: piles of straw turning into soft golden threads. MOOD: escalating desperation, ominous bargain. STYLE: Watercolor illustration style, whimsical yet tense.

imageDescriptions.chapterTitle: Krönung, Glück und die Rückkehr des Wächters
imageDescriptions.description: HERO SHOT of a royal nursery inside the palace at soft moonlight. LIGHTING: soft silver moonlight combined with warm candle glow. FOREGROUND: a small sleeping baby wrapped in a gentle blanket; Alexander (tousled brown hair, green eyes) holding the cradle, pale and worried; Adrian (curly ginger hair, sky-blue eyes) protective beside him. MIDGROUND: Brumm the Stoneguard (stone form, glowing red aura) standing tall and solemn in the doorway. BACKGROUND: tapestries, moonlit balcony, vigilant guards. MOOD: startled grief turning to urgent resolve. STYLE: Watercolor illustration style, rich textures, warm-cool contrast.

DRAMATIC ANGLE of a moonlit forest clearing with a small fire. LIGHTING: soft moonlight through tree canopy and warm fire glow. FOREGROUND: Adrian (curly ginger hair, bright sky-blue eyes) crouched behind a mossy tree, listening intently. MIDGROUND: Brumm the Stoneguard (240cm stone form, glowing red aura) sitting by the fire, arranging pebbles and singing, small sparks rising. BACKGROUND: Ente Emma near a stream and Eichhörnchen Emma perched above, both watching. MOOD: secretive, triumphant discovery. STYLE: Watercolor illustration style, magical and whimsical, textured shadows.

imageDescriptions.chapterTitle: Die Enthüllung und das Ende des Versprechens
imageDescriptions.description: HERO SHOT of the palace great hall during the reveal moment. LIGHTING: dramatic spotlight from high windows and soft ambient candlelight. FOREGROUND: Adrian (curly ginger hair, sky-blue eyes) standing brave and vocally triumphant; Alexander (tousled brown hair, green eyes) kneeling, holding a warm, glowing small pebble. MIDGROUND: Brumm the Stoneguard reduced to a small glowing stone, cracks visible on fallen larger pieces. BACKGROUND: surprised king, curious guards, Ente Emma and Eichhörnchen Emma nearby. MOOD: triumphant, relieved, gently comic. STYLE: Watercolor illustration style, vibrant magical colors and whimsical textures.
